---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import marcportrait from '../assets/images/marcportrait.jpg';
import deana from '../assets/images/deana2.jpg';
import award2021 from '../assets/images/bestchiro2021.png';
import award2022 from '../assets/images/best-of-2022.png';
import award2024 from '../assets/images/best-chiro-2024.jpg';
import award2025 from '../assets/images/best-chiro-2025.jpg';
---
<Layout
  title="About Our Doctors | D & M Chiropractic — Upper St. Clair, PA"
  description="Meet Dr. Marc Micucci and Dr. Deana Micucci, Life University graduates and award-winning chiropractors serving Upper St. Clair, PA for over 15 years."
  canonicalPath="/about/"
  page="about"
>

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="container page-hero-content">
      <span class="section-label reveal">About Us</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero-heading reveal reveal-delay-1">Two Doctors.<br/><span class="teal-text">One Mission.</span></h1>
      <p class="page-hero-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">Dr. Marc and Dr. Deana Micucci are a husband-and-wife chiropractic team committed to helping every patient achieve lasting health — naturally, without drugs or surgery.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dr. Marc -->
  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="marc-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="doctor-layout">
        <div class="doctor-portrait reveal">
          <div class="portrait-frame">
            <Image src={marcportrait} alt="Dr. Marc Micucci, Doctor of Chiropractic" widths={[500, 800]} class="portrait-img" />
          </div>
          <div class="portrait-card">
            <p class="portrait-name">Dr. Marc Micucci, D.C.</p>
            <p class="portrait-title">Doctor of Chiropractic</p>
            <ul class="portrait-creds" aria-label="Credentials">
              <li>B.S. Exercise Physiology — West Liberty State College</li>
              <li>Doctorate of Chiropractic — Life University, Marietta, GA</li>
              <li>Pennsylvania Chiropractic License</li>
              <li>License, Adjunctive Procedures / Physical Therapy</li>
              <li>License, Chiropractic X-ray Theory and Practice</li>
              <li>Member, Pennsylvania Chiropractic Association</li>
              <li>24 Hours Continuing Education — biennial</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="doctor-bio-content reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <span class="section-label">Co-Founder</span>
          <div class="teal-line"></div>
          <h2 class="section-heading" id="marc-heading">Dr. Marc Micucci, D.C.</h2>
          <div class="bio-text">
            <p>Dr. Marc attended West Liberty State College, earning a degree in exercise physiology. Early in his career, he worked for MacPhearson Chiropractic and Therapeutic Rehab in West Virginia, where he developed specific rehabilitation programs for auto accident victims, workers' compensation cases, frozen shoulder, carpal tunnel syndrome, and spinal pain conditions.</p>
            <p>Seeing patient after patient achieve results through chiropractic care inspired him to pursue his doctorate. He and Dr. Deana enrolled at Life University in Marietta, Georgia — one of the nation's most respected chiropractic programs — where their medical education covered anatomy, physiology, neurology, orthopedics, nutrition, radiology, and more.</p>
            <p>Dr. Marc believes in two approaches to chiropractic: treating symptoms, and treating the cause. "The reason our office is so successful is that we take the second approach and correct the cause of the problem. In turn, the symptoms are alleviated."</p>
            <p>His goal is to educate and help as many people as possible — from infants to seniors — understand that a pain-free life through natural chiropractic care is achievable.</p>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="doctor-quote">
            <p>"Pain free does not mean problem free. Seeking a chiropractor early in life for routine spinal check-ups can help prevent spinal decay and the neuromuscular conditions people face every day."</p>
            <cite>— Dr. Marc Micucci, D.C.</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Dr. Deana -->
  <section class="section section-alt" aria-labelledby="deana-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="doctor-layout reverse">
        <div class="doctor-portrait reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="portrait-frame">
            <Image src={deana} alt="Dr. Deana Micucci, Doctor of Chiropractic" widths={[500, 800]} class="portrait-img" />
          </div>
          <div class="portrait-card">
            <p class="portrait-name">Dr. Deana Micucci, D.C.</p>
            <p class="portrait-title">Doctor of Chiropractic</p>
            <ul class="portrait-creds" aria-label="Credentials">
              <li>B.S. Dental Hygiene — West Liberty State College</li>
              <li>Pre-Med Coursework</li>
              <li>Doctorate of Chiropractic — Life University, Marietta, GA</li>
              <li>Pennsylvania Chiropractic License</li>
              <li>License, Adjunctive Procedures / Physical Therapy</li>
              <li>License, Chiropractic X-ray Theory and Practice</li>
              <li>Member, Pennsylvania Chiropractic Association</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="doctor-bio-content reveal">
          <span class="section-label">Co-Founder</span>
          <div class="teal-line"></div>
          <h2 class="section-heading" id="deana-heading">Dr. Deana Micucci, D.C.</h2>
          <div class="bio-text">
            <p>Dr. Deana's path to chiropractic began with personal loss. After her mother passed away from lung cancer, she found herself drawn to natural approaches that support the body's innate healing processes — rather than relying solely on conventional medicine.</p>
            <p>She had already earned her undergraduate degree in Dental Hygiene from West Liberty State College, and after working as a hygienist in Pittsburgh, she decided to pursue a deeper path. She completed her pre-med coursework and enrolled at Life University in Marietta, Georgia alongside her husband Marc.</p>
            <p>Dr. Deana's philosophy centers on achieving optimal wellness by working with the body's natural intelligence. She integrates nutritional support, physical modalities, lifestyle changes, and stress management techniques into a holistic approach to healing.</p>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="doctor-quote">
            <p>"I believe that optimal wellness is achieved by the body's innate ability to heal from the inside out. It is my goal to offer a natural approach to uncovering the underlying cause of dysfunction."</p>
            <cite>— Dr. Deana Micucci, D.C.</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Us -->
  <section class="section why-section" aria-labelledby="why-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 3rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Differentiators</span>
        <div class="teal-line" style="margin:0.75rem auto 0;"></div>
        <h2 class="section-heading" id="why-heading">Why Choose D&M Chiropractic?</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="why-grid">
        {[
          { icon: '⚡', title: 'No Wait Policy', desc: 'All of our patients are seen immediately. Your time is valuable — we respect it.' },
          { icon: '🤝', title: 'Friendly Staff', desc: 'Professional, warm, and genuinely caring. You\'ll feel welcome from your very first call.' },
          { icon: '🏥', title: 'Private Treatment Rooms', desc: 'Large, private rooms ensure your comfort and confidentiality throughout treatment.' },
          { icon: '🗺️', title: 'Convenient Location', desc: 'Easily accessible on Washington Road in Upper St. Clair with ample parking.' },
          { icon: '📋', title: 'We Handle Insurance', desc: 'Most insurance accepted. We do all the paperwork so you can focus on healing.' },
          { icon: '🔬', title: 'Corrective Care', desc: 'We correct the cause of the problem — not just mask symptoms — for lasting results.' },
          { icon: '🚗', title: 'Auto Accident Specialists', desc: 'NASA-derived spinal monitoring technology to document injuries and track recovery.' },
          { icon: '👨‍👩‍👦', title: 'Whole-Family Practice', desc: 'We treat patients from infancy through senior years. The whole family is welcome.' },
        ].map((item, i) => (
          <div class={`why-card card reveal reveal-delay-${(i % 4) + 1}`}>
            <div class="why-icon" aria-hidden="true">{item.icon}</div>
            <h3 class="why-title">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="why-desc">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Awards -->
  <section class="section section-alt awards-section" aria-labelledby="awards-about-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 3rem;">
        <span class="section-label">Recognition</span>
        <div class="teal-line" style="margin:0.75rem auto 0;"></div>
        <h2 class="section-heading" id="awards-about-heading">Award-Winning Care, Year After Year</h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0 auto;">Expertise.com evaluates thousands of Pittsburgh chiropractors on qualifications, experience, reputation, and patient reviews. D&M has earned the Best Chiropractors recognition consistently since 2018.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="awards-showcase reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <figure class="award-showcase-item">
          <Image src={award2021} alt="Expertise Best Pittsburgh Chiropractors 2021" width={180} height={180} />
          <figcaption>2021</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="award-showcase-item">
          <Image src={award2022} alt="Expertise Best Pittsburgh Chiropractors 2022" width={180} height={180} />
          <figcaption>2022</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="award-showcase-item">
          <Image src={award2024} alt="Expertise Best Pittsburgh Chiropractors 2024" width={180} height={180} />
          <figcaption>2024</figcaption>
        </figure>
        <figure class="award-showcase-item">
          <Image src={award2025} alt="Expertise Best Pittsburgh Chiropractors 2025" width={180} height={180} />
          <figcaption>2025</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>
      <p class="awards-note reveal reveal-delay-3">Also awarded in 2018, 2020, 2021, 2022, and 2023 — over 10 years of consistent recognition.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section" style="background:var(--navy-dark);" aria-labelledby="about-cta-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-cta card reveal" style="text-align:center;padding:3rem 2rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy-mid),rgba(46,184,176,0.07));">
        <h2 id="about-cta-heading" class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Meet Us in Person</h2>
        <p class="section-sub" style="margin:0 auto 2rem;">Your free consultation includes a complete evaluation by Dr. Marc or Dr. Deana — and a free MRI review if you have one. No obligation, no pressure.</p>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Book Your Free Visit</a>
          <a href="tel:+14128331101" class="btn btn-outline">Call (412) 833-1101</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 8rem 1.5rem 5rem;
    background: var(--navy-dark);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .page-hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(46,184,176,0.10) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .page-hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; }
  .page-hero-heading {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.25rem;
  }
  .teal-text { color: var(--teal); }
  .page-hero-sub { font-size: 1.0625rem; color: var(--gray-mid); max-width: 560px; }

  .section-alt { background: var(--navy-mid); }
  .section { background: var(--navy-dark); }

  .doctor-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 380px 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .doctor-layout.reverse { direction: rtl; }
  .doctor-layout.reverse > * { direction: ltr; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .doctor-layout, .doctor-layout.reverse { grid-template-columns: 1fr; direction: ltr; gap: 2.5rem; }
  }

  .portrait-frame {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(46,184,176,0.15);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .portrait-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3/4;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: top center;
    display: block;
  }
  .portrait-card {
    background: var(--navy-mid);
    border: 1px solid rgba(46,184,176,0.1);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .portrait-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .portrait-title {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--teal);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .portrait-creds { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .portrait-creds li {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    padding-left: 0.875rem;
    position: relative;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .portrait-creds li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .bio-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .bio-text p { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: var(--gray-mid); line-height: 1.8; }

  .doctor-quote {
    background: var(--teal-muted);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--teal);
    border-radius: 0 var(--radius) var(--radius) 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  .doctor-quote p {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }
  .doctor-quote cite {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) { .why-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .why-card { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .why-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
  .why-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .why-desc { font-size: 0.8125rem; color: var(--gray-mid); line-height: 1.65; }

  .awards-showcase {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .award-showcase-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .award-showcase-item img { border-radius: 12px; width: 140px; height: 140px; object-fit: contain; }
  .award-showcase-item figcaption {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--teal);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .awards-note { text-align: center; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--gray-mid); }
</style>
